<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - rby byfrḥ lmạ bạrnm wạrfʿ ṣwty ạ̹lyh
 rby byfrḥ lmạ bạqdm sẖkry wḥmdy ạ̹lyh qlby bạlthlyl ysbḥ qlby bạltsbyḥ yhll
 1- ʿlsẖạn kdh yạ ḥbyby yswʿ ạqbl ḥmdy wạltsbyḥ
 ạnạ jạylk wbkl kẖsẖwʿ ạhdy lạsmk ạḥly̱ mdyḥ
 2- wyạ yswʿ ạfrạḥy tdwm bạltrnym ạfrạḥy tzyd
 lmạ ạrnm ṭwl ạlywm qlby hạyfrḥ wạbqy̱ sʿyd
 3- gẖny yạ qlby bạlạ̉lḥạn wạrfʿ ṣwtk wạhtf qwl
 ạ̉nạ byswʿ dạymaⁿạ frḥạn hw nsẖydy hnạ ʿly̱ ṭwl</lyrics>
